⅔	<small>[symbol]</small><br><frac23/<br>two-thirds (fraction)<br>三分之二（分数）
√	<small>[symbol]</small><br><root/<br>"root" sign used in etymologies, as in original<br>“根号”，用于词源，与原版一致
≈	<small>[symbol]</small><br>double tilde ("approximately equals")<br>used by typists as a place-holder in word combinations where the capitalized headword should be<br>双波浪号（“约等于”）<br>打字员用作占位符，标示在单词组合中应填入大写的词目词
☞	<small>[symbol]</small><br><hand/<br>(the typographer's "fist")<br>Appearing as a "pointing hand" character (for explanatory notes)<br>（印刷上的“手形”标记）<br>显示为“指向手”字符（用于解释性注释）
